snippet.title: Jar Wars Official Trailer - Free VR Game - OUT NOW
snippet.description:
Jar Wars is a slap-stick multiplayer VR game. Battle with friends and foes using impractical weapons like giant rockets, a hologram sword, and boxing gloves. Will you be the last brain standing?

Discord - https://discord.gg/AhxcGZ3
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1095060/Jar_Wars/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/FarCadeCo
Website - http://farcade.com/

Out Now on Steam!
